This option is used for tracking RMI calls within a transaction.
This option is available only when using purley SpringRemote framework and Java API

Data collection are as follow

    1. RMI profile for remote call
    2. RMI call topology connection 

When this option is enabled and the RMI related classes are loaded, the following information are shown in the agent log

